snippet.title: Haunted PS1 Madvent Calendar 2020 Trailer
snippet.description:
Another shining collaboration comes to you from the haunted ps1 low rez horror community! Dive into a new game or interactive scene each day until the 24th of December here: https://hauntedps1.itch.io/madvent2020

Trailer created by z_bill, footsage gathered by Shane Yach and music by Ryan Rauch.
